      "content": "i get that, its definitely more \"formal.\" but when you say text B is too informal, do you think the use of AAVE specifically makes the writer seem less capable or less educated? like, if the person writing B was white but just using slang, would it be viewed differently by a professor than if it was someone using AAVE?",
